uration, and the instructions to avoid exposing keys to the browser, specifically the client-side Firebase key. I also need to verify that `set_up_firebase` does populate the config, so the error does suggest the user needs to update the Firebase API key, as well as ensure that I\'m also ensuring the Gemini Key is securely stored.\n\n\n"
